import React from 'react' import { connect } from 'react-redux' import { goLive } from '../actions' import { useHistory } from 'react-router-dom' function ActivateAgent(props) { const { push } = useHistory() const handelclick = () => { props.dispatch(goLive(props.porject)) props.setshowlive() push(`/dachboard/agent/${props.match.params.idpost}`) } return (
) } export default connect(null)(ActivateAgent)
